metadata.name: Astro1
metadata.description:
/ ASTRO \\

I'd like to introduce to all of you Astro. My new Cinematic Project.
This Cinematic project will have a solid roadmap and utilities which we will uncover in near future along our community growing on discord. More infos are to come but we want notify you as soon as we are ready on our instagram and twitter account.

First of all there will be a first chapter of a more complex storyline, divided in 8 parts each unveiling a different universe connected together.
 A sort of introduction. A first step and voyage into Astro’s Universe, which is expanding day after day.
I'm very proud and thankful how this project is getting everyday clearer and clearer and step after step we're getting further in developement.

Last but not least I'm really happy how team is growing and looking forward to develope all this in the next months.
In the next future we will introduce to you also all the artists, that will be involved in this project.
